bio: Rohan is a passionate web developer and educator with over 8 years of experience in front-end technologies like HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. He focuses on making coding simple and practical for beginners.
Ketan is an experienced software engineer specializing in JavaScript, Android, and full-stack development. He enjoys helping students build real-world applications through hands-on coding sessions.

Prof. Sameer has over 25 years of academic and industry experience in computer science. He specializes in software architecture, data science, and mentoring aspiring developers to excel in technology careers.
Amit is an upcoming UI/UX designer passionate about creating user-friendly interfaces. With a background in computer applications, he aims to combine aesthetics and usability in digital products.
